<div class="page-content">
    <div class="page-header">
        <h1>Messages</h1>
        <a href="#add" class="btn btn-primary" data-route="/Application/Messages/Form">
            <span>+</span> Write Message
        </a>
    </div>

    <p class="page-description">Personal messages attached to your gifts. These will be delivered along with the gift.</p>

    <div class="messages-list" id="messages-list">
        <div class="card message-card">
            <div class="message-header">
                <span class="message-for">For: Emily Johnson</span>
                <span class="message-occasion">Birthday</span>
            </div>
            <div class="message-preview">
                "Happy Birthday, sweetheart! Even though I can't be there in person, 
                know that I'm celebrating you today..."
            </div>
            <div class="message-footer">
                <span class="message-attached">Attached to: Birthday Flowers</span>
                <div class="message-actions">
                    <button class="btn btn-ghost btn-sm">Edit</button>
                    <button class="btn btn-ghost btn-sm">Preview</button>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="card message-card">
            <div class="message-header">
                <span class="message-for">For: Emily Johnson</span>
                <span class="message-occasion">Graduation</span>
            </div>
            <div class="message-preview">
                "I'm so incredibly proud of you. Watching you grow into the person you are today 
                has been one of my greatest joys..."
            </div>
            <div class="message-footer">
                <span class="message-attached">Attached to: Graduation Watch</span>
                <div class="message-actions">
                    <button class="btn btn-ghost btn-sm">Edit</button>
                    <button class="btn btn-ghost btn-sm">Preview</button>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="card message-card">
            <div class="message-header">
                <span class="message-for">For: Michael Johnson</span>
                <span class="message-occasion">Christmas</span>
            </div>
            <div class="message-preview">
                "Merry Christmas, son! These books shaped who I am, and I hope they'll 
                bring you as much joy and wisdom as they brought me..."
            </div>
            <div class="message-footer">
                <span class="message-attached">Attached to: Book Collection</span>
                <div class="message-actions">
                    <button class="btn btn-ghost btn-sm">Edit</button>
                    <button class="btn btn-ghost btn-sm">Preview</button>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
